    • Constructor Detail

      • Villager

        public Villager(String name,
                boolean inSect,
                int scepticism,
                int selfEsteem,
                int selfAwareness,
                int argSkills,
                String profession)
        The constructor is given the name, the profession and the values for the attributes as parameters.
        Parameters:
        name - CreateVillagers picks a name from the list created by Config.
        inSect - Initial value is false, ie. the villager is not a member.
        scepticism - CreateVillagers picks a number that is base+random.
        selfEsteem - CreateVillagers picks a number that is base+random.
        selfAwareness - CreateVillagers picks a number that is base+random.
        argSkills - CreateVillagers picks a number that is base+random.
        profession - CreateVillagers picks a name from the list created by Config.
